title: Teemoing special icon
body: For some reason when I try to play it cuts the game in half (I play on a laptop) and I can still click the button but the counter doesn't go up. Is this just me? My friend clicked on the link and said it was fine and when he screen-shared me on skype it was the full thing.

replies.body:
Try a different browser or by [clearing your browser's cache](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) to see if it resolves this.

Let me know if you have any other questions.
